Package org.apache.openjpa.meta

Class QueryMetaData

java.lang.Object
org.apache.openjpa.meta.QueryMetaData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, SourceTracker, Commentable, MetaDataModes
Direct Known Subclasses:
MultiQueryMetaData
public class QueryMetaData extends Object implements MetaDataModes, SourceTracker, Commentable, Serializable
Holds metadata about named queries. Information stored in this instance gets transfered to new Query instances.
Author:
Steve Kim
